<section id="xml_exampleTranslation">
    <title>Element: <literal>&lt;exampleTranslation&gt;</literal></title>
    <para>Implements the <olink targetptr="xlingual_exampleTranslation">exampleTranslation</olink> object type from the Crosslingual Module.</para>

    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Attributes</title>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>@language</literal> <glossterm>optional</glossterm> if the ancestor <literal>&lt;lexicographicResource&gt;</literal>
                contains exactly one <literal>&lt;translationLanguage&gt;</literal>,
                <glossterm>required</glossterm> otherwise</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>@soundFile</literal>
                <glossterm>optional</glossterm></para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    
    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Child elements</title>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>&lt;text&gt;</literal> <glossterm>required</glossterm> (exactly one). If implementing the Annotation Module
                <literal>&lt;text&gt;</literal> can contain a mixture of plain text, 
                <literal><olink targetptr="xml_headwordMarker">&lt;headwordMarker&gt;</olink></literal> elements
                and <literal><olink targetptr="xml_collocateMarker">&lt;collocateMarker&gt;</olink></literal> elements.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal><olink targetptr="xml_label">&lt;label&gt;</olink></literal> <glossterm>optional</glossterm> (zero or more)</para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    
    
</section>
